":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第十五次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXiZpgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXiZpgg.png&h=5288b347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8k1CBg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8k1CBg.png&h=eddab2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxRoMgT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxRoMgT.png&h=2ef27a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjJq3Fy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjJq3Fy.png&h=f22a8d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">806.24</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">19.38</span>%<br />\n(睇黎HP已在800企穩)<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第十六波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為理想進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營，二軍為一周長期戰線赤兔部隊。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團註明兩軍進軍方向提議<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領主流意見<br />\n2. 操作選取軍師兵士們主流意見之數隻股票站上點將台點將後ALL IN買入。<br />\n3. <span class=\"red\">一軍買入時間預計為盤中12:00前。</span><br />\n4. 一軍陷陣營不買入妹十世股，二軍赤兔隊不選擇QQQ<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、盤後07:45或開市緊急調動<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位，若為QQQ 上下限改為3%。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機向數名選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第十五次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2449708/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2449708/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呂布止盈機智戰勝GME，武力100 智力75操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mD3CaXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmD3CaXB.jpg&h=a3a7623d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"今晚一定冇事 買反向vix SVXY!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"-0.5倍第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924e9699e103431af53e92367298708e3be4a4f1","tid":2450743,"uid":61032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91ae8c4c9c3018756f96648b49d1dc285a7509b1","tid":2450743,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"點將台現時排名<br />\n1.AMC 2.VWAGY 3.SOS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"點解要燈AMC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b030f50dfb7d7f01621ef892ed92feb109a838","tid":2450743,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b5190c31c76483ef9b89dfe72522686e4d327a3","tid":2450743,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a9d98cb4a2b1e484f7a6874f29e1dd4baac4ed","tid":2450743,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"今日amc應該橫行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"此話何解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"上15有阻力，早兩日俾gme累街坊明明大利好升到16都跌返落黎，而家利好因素早已price in，橫行機會較大<br />\n<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"8cea67a8feace1beed47c4fa9c2f27072844b097","tid":2450743,"uid":178068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dec9c6560d270fd02598d2cdc1f0bd7cdd75fea","tid":2450743,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d237e70e731ef6bddfe4d5ccc2436e9c17ca57","tid":2450743,"uid":178068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa57a6f01471c995bd698fd5ca506edb0268872c","tid":2450743,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"